<h3>2.1.14查询国标设备</h3>
<div class="knife4j-word-api">
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口地址</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><span class="knife4j-word-method">GET</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>/api/device/query/devices/{deviceId}</code></div>
