<h3>2.1.21设备报警查询</h3>
<div class="knife4j-word-api">
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口地址</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><span class="knife4j-word-method">GET</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>/api/device/query/alarm</code></div>
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口描述</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"></div>
<div class="knife4j-word-title">请求数据类型</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><code>application/x-www-form-urlencoded</code></div>
<div class="knife4j-word-title">响应数据类型</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><code>*/*</code></div>


<div class="knife4j-word-title">请求参数</div><br/>
<div class="knife4j-word-content">
<table class="knife4j-word-table">
<thead><tr><th>参数名称</th><th>参数说明</th><th>请求类型</th><th>必须</th><th>数据类型</th><th>schema</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>deviceId</td>
<td>设备国标编号</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>true</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>startPriority</td>
<td>报警起始级别, 0为全部,1为一级警情,2为二级警情,3为三级警情,4为四级警情</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>endPriority</td>
<td>报警终止级别, ,0为全部,1为一级警情,2为二级警情,3为三级警情,4为四级警情</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>alarmMethod</td>
<td>报警方式条件,取值0为全部,1为电话报警,2为设备报警,3为短信报警,4为GPS报警,5为视频报警,6为设备故障报警,7其他报警;可以为直接组合如12为电话报警或设备报警</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>alarmType</td>
<td>报警类型</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>startTime</td>
<td>报警发生起始时间</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>endTime</td>
<td>报警发生终止时间</td>
<td>query</td>
<td>false</td>
<td>string</td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>


