<h3>2.9.6推流列表查询</h3>
<div class="knife4j-word-api">
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口地址</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><span class="knife4j-word-method">GET</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>/api/push/list</code></div>
