<td>integer(int32)</td>
<td>integer(int32)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>gbSvcTimeSupportMode</td>
<td>国标-时域编码能力,取值0-不支持;1-1级增强;2-2级增强;3-3级增强(可选)</td>
<td>integer(int32)</td>
<td>integer(int32)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
