<h3>2.27.4获取历史媒体下载进度</h3>
<div class="knife4j-word-api">
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口地址</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><span class="knife4j-word-method">GET</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>/api/gb_record/download/progress/{deviceId}/{channelId}/{stream}</code></div>
