<h3>2.31.2基本配置设置命令</h3>
<div class="knife4j-word-api">
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口地址</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"><span class="knife4j-word-method">GET</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>/api/device/config/basicParam</code></div>
<div class="knife4j-word-title">接口描述</div>
<div class="knife4j-word-content"></div>
